Package: powerbrmsINLA
Title: Bayesian Power Analysis Using 'brms' and 'INLA'
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Tony Myers
Maintainer: Tony Myers <admyers@aol.com>
Description: Provides tools for Bayesian power analysis and assurance 
    calculations using the statistical frameworks of 'brms' and 'INLA'. 
    Includes simulation-based approaches, support for multiple decision 
    rules (direction, threshold, ROPE), sequential designs, and 
    visualisation helpers.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
